@startuml
title BP-06 - Grade and Class Setup

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Academic Staff|
start
:Create grade level;
:Create class within grade;
:Assign homeroom or metadata if available;

|Platform|
:Validate tenant scope;
:Validate grade code uniqueness;
:Validate class code uniqueness within grade;

if (Configuration valid?) then (Yes)
  :Save grade and class configuration;
else (No)
  :Return validation error;
  stop
endif

|Academic Staff|
:Use class data for student registration and bulk billing selection;
stop

note right
Future billing usage:
Bulk bill generation can target a class, grade,
or academic period once academic modules exist.
end note
@enduml
